{"title":"氍毹三叹","authors":["蔡若虹"],"dates":[{"year":1988,"month":1,"day":28}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"氍毹三叹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（菩萨蛮）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蔡若虹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一、观舞剧《铜雀伎》"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铿锵一面多情鼓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"翩翩红袖随声舞；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同命更同心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"知心听鼓音。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不忘铜雀耻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"辗转红颜死；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千古恨难平，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"惊雷鼓上鸣！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二、观歌剧《原野》"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脚镣已断心镣在，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深沉仇恨深沉爱；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仇与爱相跟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"复仇殃子孙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手中刀一握，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心上冤魂哭；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"原野寂无声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"盲然看死生！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三、观豫剧《石头梦》"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"逃荒人作荒唐梦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石头会比黄金重；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"原想一头牛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忽成阶下囚！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"独轮车已去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世上无悲剧；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"何物弄沉浮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"空山多石头！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}